OL,3,CKeir Starmer's departure 'brutal and
OL,4,Cdisappointing', says ally Chris Ward
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer's departure is
OL,7,F'brutal' and 'disappointing',
OL,8,Faccording to one of his closest allies
OL,9,Fin politics.
OL,11,FChris Ward worked for the prime
OL,12,Fminister as a speechwriter and
OL,13,Fparliamentary aide, before being
OL,14,Fpromoted to Cabinet Office minister.
OL,16,F"Obviously, on a personal level, I'm
OL,17,Fvery disappointed about today, but on
OL,18,Fa political level as well. I think
OL,19,Fwe've been making big progress in the
OL,20,Ffirst two years.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
