OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782206307
OL,3,CKeir Starmer's departure 'brutal and
OL,4,Cdisappointing', says ally Chris Ward
OL,6,F"On child poverty, on waiting lists,
OL,7,Fon immigration. He's got a record, I
OL,8,Fthink, to be proud of. But politics is
OL,9,Fa brutal game."
OL,11,FThe Brighton Kemptown and Peacehaven
OL,12,FMP added: "You've got to remember,
OL,13,Fwhen he became leader, he took over a
OL,14,Fparty that was broken after four
OL,15,Fdefeats.
OL,17,F"It was morally bankrupt, infested
OL,18,Fwith anti-Semitism. He turned that
OL,19,Fround. He put us back on path to win a
OL,20,Fgeneral election, and won it by
OL,21,Flandslide."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]tD@KOUyD@AOU}D@KO]
