OL,3,CKeir Starmer's departure 'brutal and
OL,4,Cdisappointing', says ally Chris Ward
OL,6,FOther Labour MPs representing
OL,7,Fconstituencies in the South and South
OL,8,FEast of England have been less
OL,9,Fcomplimentary about Sir Keir's record
OL,10,Fin Downing Street.
OL,12,FNeil Duncan-Jordan, who has
OL,13,Frepresented Poole in Dorset since
OL,14,F2024, told ITV News Meridian: "There
OL,15,Fhave been a number of errors over a
OL,16,Fnumber of months and years right from
OL,17,Fvery early on with the winter fuel
OL,18,Fallowance debacle."
OL,26,@vD@_OUzD@SO]
