OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782206307
OL,3,CKeir Starmer's departure 'brutal and
OL,4,Cdisappointing', says ally Chris Ward
OL,6,FThe Labour backbencher added: "One of
OL,7,Fthe real problems with Keir's
OL,8,Fleadership is nobody could tell you
OL,9,Fwhat it was. He famously said there's
OL,10,Fno such thing as 'Starmerism', and
OL,11,Ftherein lies the problem."
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer will stay on as prime
OL,14,Fminister until a new Labour leader is
OL,15,Fselected. Nominations for that
OL,16,Fposition are due to open on 9 July.
OL,26,@nD@_OUsD@ZO]
